3422,"uid":40250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T00:44:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>認真啲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你改個咁既名點同你認真呀"},{"pid":"3077ac5776b6b81494085a940f3e56af91193f0f","tid":173422,"uid":92534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T01:41:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你個ex都幾仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢想追返我 我唔受佢氹 可能老羞成怒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過呢句真係好hurt<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我知 佢一直掛住同ex既點滴<br />\n我知 我一直比唔上佢ex <br />\n我知 我只係一個唔盡責既水泡 替代品<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56469a46644195098e5b0a459cef121db344af9f","tid":173422,"uid":92534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T01:44:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>得閒買下啲野食日用品俾佢<br />\n玩下啲小驚喜 可能係啲公仔都夠<br />\n接下收工咁</blockquote><br />\n有呀 之前每次見親佢都買佢中意既口味既野食比佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但佢食完就唔記得 我之前有問過佢好無食之類<br />\n佢係成件事唔記得左<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我仲專登懶係小驚喜收埋落袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 原來多舊魚"},{"pid":"5f5ffeb6e8637aa3f240d0e850b8f80fd35a7712","tid":173422,"uid":41974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T01:46:06.000Z","msg":"